          .form-row
            .col-md-12
              label.form-label(for='general_subtitle') 子標題
              input#general_subtitle.form-control.form-bind-data(type='text' name="general_subtitle" value='' required='')
              .valid-feedback
                | OK!
              .invalid-feedback
                | 不得為空
          .form-row
            .col-md-12
              label.form-label(for='general_loadMoreButton') 載入更多文章按鈕名稱
              input#general_loadMoreButton.form-control.form-bind-data(type='text' name="general_loadMoreButton" value='' required='')
              .valid-feedback
                | OK!
              .invalid-feedback
                | 不得為空
          .form-row
            .col-md-12
              label.form-label(for='general_filterTitle') 選擇文章類型按鈕名稱
